      "ResourceName": null,
      "Children": [
        {
          "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
          "Text": "Reference: Lake, Lachlan, and Victor O. Sadras. ‘Lentil Yield and Crop Growth Rate Are Coupled under Stress but Uncoupled under Favourable Conditions’. European Journal of Agronomy 126 (1 May 2021): 126266. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.eja.2021.126266.\n\nPant material, environments and experimental design:\n\nWe established a factorial experiment with 20 lentil lines varying in seed type and phenology.\n\nCrops were grown in eight environments that resulted from the combinationof two seasons (2018, 2019), two sowing dates and two water regimes. Early sowings were on the 24th of April 2018 and the 29th April 2019, and the late sowings on the 6th of June 2018 and 24th of June 2019. Early-sown crops were irrigated or rainfed. Rainout shelters were set on earlysown crops to exclude rainfall from 26th June 2018 to harvest and from 1st August 2019 to harvest. Late-sown crops were irrigated or rainfed.\n\nEach experimental plot comprised six rows, 0.23m apart, 5m long, with target plant density 120 plants/m2.\n\nCrops were sown after barley on calcic luvisol soil at Roseworthy (34.35, 138.69), South Australia. At sowing, we added 80kg/h amonoammonium phosphate. \n\nDaily weather data were obtained from the Roseworthy weather station of the Australian Bureau of Meteorology. The amount of irrigation was added to the rainfall of the correponding date in the daily weather data, and the rainfall was set to 0 during rainout period.",
          "Name": "Memo",
          "ResourceName": null,
          "Children": [],
          "Enabled": true,
          "ReadOnly": false
        },
        {
          "$type": "Models.Factorial.Factors, Models",
          "Name": "Factors",
          "ResourceName": null,
          "Children": [
            {
              "$type": "Models.Factorial.Permutation, Models",
              "Name": "Permutation",
              "ResourceName": null,
              "Children": [
                {
                  "$type": "Models.Factorial.Factor, Models",
                  "Specification": "",
                  "Name": "_Treat",
                  "ResourceName": null,
                  "Children": [
                    {
                      "$type": "Models.Factorial.CompositeFactor, Models",
                      "Specifications": [
                        "[Sowing].Script.SowDate=24-Apr",
                        "[IrrigationApplications]"
                      ],
                      "Paths": null,
                      "Values": null,
                      "Name": "24Apr2018Irrigated",
                      "ResourceName": null,
                      "Children": [
                        {
                          "$type": "Models.Operations, Models",
                          "Operation": [
                            {
                              "$type": "Models.Operation, Models",
                              "Enabled": true,
                              "Date": "2018-06-01",
                              "Action": "[Irrigation].Apply (35);",
                              "Line": "2018-06-01 [Irrigation].Apply (35);"
                            }
                          ],
                          "Name": "IrrigationApplications",
                          "ResourceName": null,
                          "Children": [],
